    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Impoverished or on the run, you spent your formative years living in the sewers of a major city. There, you learned lessons that have served you well, although the miasma of the sewers did permanent damage to your health. </p><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> You can automatically climb or swim (your choice) at full speed while moving, and you never get lost while underground. Additionally, while in a city with sewers, you and your companions can move from place to place without being detected, as the Director determines. </p><p><strong>Drawback:</strong> You have poison weakness 5.</p>",
      "director": ""
    },
